- select My Profile tab at the top;
- find the Special Programs tab and tap it;
- select the one you want to set up ‚Üí hit Next ‚Üí choose one or more options, then click Save;
- restart the app to apply the changes.
Feel free to get back to us at gethelp@betterme.world in case you have any other questions or requests. We are just one message away. Kind regards, team BetterMe", 'modified': '2022-11-24T09:27:31Z'}

