The Health app is not available for iPads, for this reason, Step Tracker and Statistics features are not available on it. For more assistance, please reach us at gethelp@betterme.world. Best Regards, Team BetterMe", 'modified': '2023-08-25T08:13:15Z'}

{'id': 29903872, 'body': "Hello! Thank you for your feedback!
