Moreover, you can now easily keep track of your customs activities like walking, running, cycling, dancing, and others (open the BetterMe app; go to the Plan tab; select the Do your workout option; tap Add a Custom Activity). 

This library is constantly being extended and new activities are being added. Hopefully, weightlifting will be available soon too. Appreciate your understanding!

Also, you can change measuring units:
1. Tap More ‚Üí Profile icon in the top right corner and scroll to the bottom of the page;
2. Open My Profile and you will see Units there;
3. Tap Units and select the desired ones;
4. Restart the app.
Please contact our friendly team at gethelp@betterme.world. We will be glad to answer any of your questions and explain all the needed aspects.

